What rights do you have?
Your personal information belongs to you, and we will make sure your rights are respected. You can contact us at
fundrivegames@gmail.com
at any time to ask for a copy of your data, to withdraw your consent, or to obtain the deletion of the information we keep for you.
Consent withdrawal and opt-out of sale of information
You can change your consent status at any time from the Privacy Settings available in Fun Drive Games mobile games and applications.
Please note that if Fun Drive Games does not sell the personal information of its users, we may share it with third parties such as analytics and advertising companies in order to improve and personalize your experience and adapt the content and ads of our services.
